---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const pageTitle = "Work";
---

<BaseLayout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
  <p class="mb-10">
    I'm currently available for contract or permanent work in the Boston area.
    I'd <a href="/contact">love to talk</a> if you think my experience would be a
    good fit.
  </p>
  <hr class="mb-10" />

  <h2 class="mb-2">Michael P. LeRoux</h2>
  <p class="mb-0">Somerville, MA</p>
  <p class="mb-4">
    LinkedIn: <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/michaelleroux"
      >linkedin.com/in/michaelleroux</a
    > • GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/mpleroux"> github.com/mpleroux </a>
  </p>

  <h3 class="pt-3">SUMMARY</h3>

  <p>
    Software Engineer with 10+ years of experience and a strong focus on
    building polished, consistent user interfaces. Proven track record of
    collaborating with cross-functional teams to streamline content workflows
    and bridge technical gaps. Dedicated to maintainable code, clear
    documentation, and contributing to a collaborative engineering culture.
    Currently leveraging a professional background in <span class="font-medium"
      >JavaScript</span
    > and
    <span class="font-medium">TypeScript</span>
    to expand my toolkit with <span class="font-medium">React</span>, <span
      class="font-medium">Next.js</span
    >, <span class="font-medium"> Astro </span>, and AI-assisted tools.
  </p>

